==English==

===Noun===
'''[[machine]] [[translation]]'''

# {{translation studies}} The act of [[translate|translating]] something by means of a [[machine]], especially a [[computer]].
# {{translation studies}} The act of translating a [[computer language]] into a form more directly usable by the computer.

====Related terms====
* [[automatic translation]] ''(mostly used by non-native speakers)''
* [[computer assisted translation]] ''(partial synonym)''
* [[machine-aided translation]] ''(partial synonym)''
* [[machine translator]]
* [[mechanical translation]] {{obsolete}}
* [[MT]] {{abbreviation}}

